===34街車站===
自2013年12月以後開始施工的[[34街-哈德遜調車場車站_(IRT法拉盛線)|34街車站]]位於十一大道與34街街口，在地鐵7號線延伸段通車後會成為其唯一一座新站，預計在2014年6月開通。紐約大都會運輸署表示，該站將會使周邊地區的「新樓房、餐廳和娛樂場所開始增加」，鄰近地帶除了[[地獄廚房_(曼哈頓)|地獄廚房]]之外還包括[[切爾西_(曼哈頓)|切爾西]]<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.mta.info/capital/future/extension.php  |title= 7 Line Extension |author=Staff writer(s) |date= |publisher=[[紐約大都會運輸署|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]] |accessdate=2013-07-03}}</ref>。

===第十大道車站===
儘管地鐵7號線的延伸計畫中原先有包含41街上的{{Link-en|第十大道車站 (IRT法拉盛線)|10th Avenue (IRT Flushing Line)|第十大道車站}}，然而時報廣場和34街中間的設站計畫卻在2007年10月時因成本升高而遭到剔除，只剩下34街的終點站。大都會運輸署表示除非能取得足夠資金，否則不可能在延伸計畫中追加這座車站<ref name="ny1-2007-10-25"/>。因此2007年的施工合約中並沒有包含該站的興建，但仍被列為一個耗資4億5千萬美元的選擇方案，2007年12月下旬的一份報告指出，如果紐約市府和大都會運輸署能對額外的經費達成協議，便可以先行施作第十大道車站的部分站體<ref>{{Cite news |title=7 Line Extension May Get 41st Street Stop |first=Marlene |last=Naanes |url=http://www.amny.com/news/local/am-mta1221,0,632084.story |newspaper={{Link-en|AM New York|AM New York|amNewYork}} |date=2007-12-20 |accessdate=2010-02-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090513011927/http://www.amny.com/news/local/am-mta1221,0,632084.story |archivedate=2009-05-13 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。大都會運輸署在2009年2月，宣稱若是在政府能從[[2009年美國復甦與再投資法案|聯邦經濟刺激計畫]]中獲取充足財源的前提下，就會著手興建第十大道車站<ref>{{Cite news|title=Will the Stimulus Save 7 Extension Stop? |first=Benjamin |last=Kabak |url=http://secondavenuesagas.com/2009/02/02/will-the-stimulus-save-7-extension-stop/ |work=Second Ave. Sagas  |date=2009-02-02 |accessdate=2010-02-28}}</ref>。2010年6月，紐約市宣布市府正在尋求資金，以對於第十大道車站的設置進行[[可行性研究|可行性研究]]，而擬定的設站方式是延後通車，設置兩座不能在地下連通的[[側式月台|側式月台]]，並各自配置一個出入口<ref>{{Cite news |title=Outcry Emerges for 41st St. Stop on New 7-Line |first=Theresa |last=Agovino |url=http://www.crainsnewyork.com/article/20100216/FREE/100219925 |newspaper={{Link-en|Crain Communications|Crain Communications|Crain's New York Business}} |date=2010-02-16 |accessdate=2010-04-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100218115623/http://www.crainsnewyork.com/article/20100216/FREE/100219925 |archivedate=2010年2月18日 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=West Side Developers Fight For 7 Line Extension |first=Jill |last=Urban |url=http://www.ny1.com/1-all-boroughs-news-content/ny1_living/116312/west-side-developers-fight-for-7-line-extension |work={{Link-en|NY1新聞|NY1|NY1}} |date=2010-04-02 |accessdate=2010-04-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100417140042/http://www.ny1.com/1-all-boroughs-news-content/ny1_living/116312/west-side-developers-fight-for-7-line-extension/ |archivedate=2010-04-17 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=City Officials Seek Federal Assistance For 7 Subway Extension |url=http://manhattan.ny1.com/content/top_stories/117672/city-officials-seek-federal-assistance-for-7-subway-extension |work={{Link-en|NY1新聞|NY1|NY1}} |date=2010-04-27 |accessdate=2010-04-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100531155214/http://manhattan.ny1.com/content/top_stories/117672/city-officials-seek-federal-assistance-for-7-subway-extension |archivedate=2010年5月31日 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=City Considering 10th Avenue Stop For 7 Train |url=http://www.ny1.com/content/top_stories/120156/city-considering-10th-avenue-stop-for-7-train |work={{Link-en|NY1新聞|NY1|NY1}} |date=2010-06-10 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120927055352/http://www.ny1.com/content/top_stories/120156/city-considering-10th-avenue-stop-for-7-train |archivedate=2012-09-27 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Mayor Applies For Funds To Redesign 7 Train Extension |url=http://manhattan.ny1.com/content/top_stories/121366/mayor-applies-for-funds-to-redesign-7-train-extension |work={{Link-en|NY1新聞|NY1|NY1}} |date=2010-06-30 |accessdate=2010-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110714220335/http://manhattan.ny1.com/content/top_stories/121366/mayor-applies-for-funds-to-redesign-7-train-extension |archivedate=2011-07-14 }}</ref>。

==紐澤西延伸計畫==
2010年11月16日，《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》報導稱彭博市府正在進行一項規畫，打算將地鐵7號線延伸到[[哈德遜河|哈德遜河]]對岸的[[紐澤西州|紐澤西州]]，於該州境內的[[霍博肯_(紐澤西州)|霍博肯]]和{{Link-en|錫考克斯樞紐站|Secaucus Junction}}等地設站，藉此與[[紐澤西公共運輸公司|紐澤西公共運輸公司]]營運的通勤鐵道轉乘，並使紐澤西的通勤族可以搭車直達曼哈頓東側的[[大中央車站|大中央車站]]，或是換搭紐約地鐵系統上的其他路線<ref>{{Cite news |title=Take the No. 7 to Secaucus? |first=Bagli |last=Charles V. |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/17/nyregion/17tunnel.html |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=2010-11-17 |accessdate=2013-07-03 |archive-date=2010-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101118062720/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/17/nyregion/17tunnel.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。若該延伸計畫實現，將是紐約地鐵有史以來第一次將服務範圍擴張到[[紐約州|紐約州]]之外，也會使7號線成為跨州地鐵。此外，亦將取代同樣穿過哈德遜河、但於2010年10月被紐澤西州州長[[克里斯·克里斯帝|克里斯·克里斯帝]]取消的{{Link-en|區域中心連通鐵路|Access to the Region's Core}}（{{lang|en|ARC}}）<ref>{{Cite news |title=New York Studies Extending Subway Line to New Jersey |first=Charles |last=Bagli |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/17/nyregion/17tunnel.html |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=2010-11-16 |accessdate=2010-11-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101118062720/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/17/nyregion/17tunnel.html |archivedate=2010年11月18日 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

2011年2月2日，紐約市的經濟開發公司通過投票，要將隧道延伸[[可行性研究|可行性研究]]的預算追加至25萬美元，而負責從事此評估案的業者——[[栢誠集團|栢誠集團]]，即為曾經協助ARC鐵路規劃過河隧道的主要廠商<ref>{{cite web   | last = Bernstein   | first = Andrea   | authorlink =    | coauthors =    | title = City finally puts $$$ behind subway to New Jersey   | work =    | publisher = Transportation Nation   | date = 2011-02-04   | url = http://transportationnation.org/2011/02/04/city-finally-puts-behind-subway-to-new-jersey/   | doi =    | accessdate = 2011-02-07   | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110206082530/http://transportationnation.org/2011/02/04/city-finally-puts-behind-subway-to-new-jersey/   | archivedate = 2011年2月6日   | deadurl = no   }}</ref><ref>{{cite web   | last = New York City Economic Development Commission   | first =    | authorlink =    | coauthors =    | title =  No. 7 Line Extension to Secaucus Consultant Services   | work =    | publisher = www.scribd.com   | date = 2011-02-02   | url = http://www.scribd.com/doc/48185181/No-7-Extension-Executive-Committee-Item-Final-Draft-2   | format = PDF   | doi =    | accessdate = 2011-02-07}}</ref>。報告結果在2013年4月出爐<ref>{{cite news   | last = Frasinelli   | first = Mike   | title = Plan to extend No. 7 subway from NYC to New Jersey could be back on track   | newspaper = The Star-Ledger   | date = 2013-04-10   | url = http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2013/04/plan_to_extend_no_7_city_subwa.html   | accessdate = 2013-04-10   | quote = }}</ref><ref>{{cite news   | last = Rouse   | first = Karen   | title = Report: Extending NY No. 7 subway line to Secaucus would accommodate commuter demand   | newspaper = The Record   | date = 2013-04-10   | url = http://www.northjersey.com/news/NY_No_7_Subway_to_Secaucus.html   | accessdate = 2013-04-10   | quote =    | archive-date = 2013-04-13   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130413011350/http://www.northjersey.com/news/NY_No_7_Subway_to_Secaucus.html   | dead-url = no   }}</ref>，內容除了{{Link-en|第十大道車站 (IRT法拉盛線)|10th Avenue (IRT Flushing Line)|第十大道車站}}的興建之外，還讓地鐵7號線的過河路線採取與ARC舊計畫相同的走線，並在錫考克斯樞紐站附近興建雙層的{{Link-en|多式運輸|Multimodal transport|多業者共駛}}路段，或是考慮拓寬[[東北走廊|東北走廊]]高鐵的路軌區，以在旁邊鋪設地鐵軌道讓列車行走<ref name="nycedc 1">{{cite report   | author= Parsons Brinkerhoff   | title = No 7 Secaucus Extension Feasibility Analysis Final Report | publisher = NYCEDC   | date = April 2013   | url = http://www.nycedc.com/sites/default/files/filemanager/Resources/Studies/No_7_Secaucus_Extension_Final_Report_April_2013.pdf   | format = PDF   | accessdate = 2013-04-10 | page = 1 }}</ref>。

根據《[[紐約郵報|紐約郵報]]》報導，倘若地鐵7號線要通至錫考克斯，就需要再2012年底取得彭博市府的正式同意。紐澤西州的克里斯帝州長和[[紐約與新澤西港務局|紐新港務局]]則公開支持此計畫，而且兩者在地鐵獲得了官方批准之後，還會幫忙分攤原先預估的100億元總經費<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.nypost.com/p/news/local/manhattan/mayor_aboard_subway_to_nj_iA2sZ3IMDdLKJYx7XCxGSI| title=Mayor aboard subway to NJ (Supports No. 7 extension to Secaucus)| work=[[紐約郵報|New York Post]]| first=Josh| last=Margolin| date=2011-10-26| accessdate=2011-10-26}}</ref>。

地鐵7號線的延伸經費比ARC隧道的興建便宜，因為前者從{{Link-en|第十一大道|Eleventh Avenue (Manhattan)}}的車站南下之後，就會轉往西邊過河，而不需要在[[先驅廣場|先驅廣場]]下方開挖複雜的深層站體，也取消了地鐵東延往該廣場時所需的昂貴隧道工事。然而與ARC方案相較之下，7號線方案從紐澤西前往曼哈頓的時間會更加拉長，因為紐澤西通勤鐵道的乘客必須去錫考克斯才能轉地鐵。另外，由於通勤列車能行走現有的過河鐵道前往[[紐約賓州車站|紐約賓州車站]]，因此地鐵7號線將無法達成分流、舒緩過河交通擁擠的關鍵目標。但另一方面，新路線如同克里斯帝州長所述，「將能讓我們（紐澤西州）直接通往曼哈頓東城，正如以往所希望的...」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.wnyc.org/articles/wnyc-news/2010/nov/16/mayor-bloomberg-explores-extending-subway-new-jersey/|title=Mayor Bloomberg Explores Extending Subway to New Jersey|publisher={{Link-en|WNYC|WNYC}}|first=Andrea|last=Bernstein|date=2010-11-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101120020352/http://www.wnyc.org/articles/wnyc-news/2010/nov/16/mayor-bloomberg-explores-extending-subway-new-jersey/|archivedate=2010-11-20}}</ref>。彭博市長已經與[[紐約州州長|紐約州州長]][[安德魯·庫默|安德魯·庫默]]會晤，而該項仍需歷時五年才能發展成形的地鐵工程並無法自動符合資格，已取得聯邦分配給ARC隧道的資金<ref>{{cite news|url=http://transportationnation.org/2010/11/17/bloomberg-new-tunnel-could-be-even-better-than-arc/#more-8561|title=Bloomberg: New Tunnel Could Be "Even Better" Than ARC|publisher={{Link-en|WNYC|WNYC}}|work=Transportation Nation|first=Jim|last=O'Grady|date=2010-11-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://newyork.cbslocal.com/2010/11/17/nyc-subway-line-may-continue-into-n-j/|title=NJ Commuters Like 7 Train Extension Plan|publisher={{Link-en|WCBS-TV|WCBS-TV|WCBS}}|date=2010-11-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nbcnewyork.com/news/local-beat/Tunnel-to-Nowhere-Might-Become-7-to-Secaucus-108680929.html|title=Tunnel to Nowhere Might Become 7 to Secaucus|publisher={{Link-en|WNBC|WNBC}}|date=2010-11-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://abclocal.go.com/wabc/video?id=7794331|title=7 Subway Extension to NJ (Video)|publisher={{Link-en|WABC-TV|WABC-TV|WABC}}|first=Jaime|last=Roth|date=2010-11-17|access-date=2014-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629045224/http://abclocal.go.com/wabc/video?id=7794331|archive-date=2011-06-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

除了地鐵7號線過河案外，[[美鐵|美鐵]]在2011年2月宣布的「{{Link-en|關口計畫|Gateway Project}}」中納入了一條連接紐澤西賓州車站至曼哈頓賓州車站的高鐵延伸計畫，旨在增強[[紐澤西通勤鐵路|紐澤西通勤鐵路]]的載客能力，而該條新鐵路的配套措施就是將地鐵7號線從34街車站向東延三個街區到賓州車站，而非如原先規劃的往西延伸過河去錫考克斯<ref name=GatewayPDF>{{cite web| page =7| last =| first =| authorlink =| coauthors =| title =Gateway Project| work =| publisher =Amtrak| date =February 2011| url =http://lautenberg.senate.gov/assets/Gateway.pdf| format =PDF| doi =| accessdate =2011-02-07| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20110207210953/http://lautenberg.senate.gov/assets/Gateway.pdf| archivedate =2011年2月7日| deadurl =yes}}</ref>。[[美國國會|美國國會]]已於2011年11月撥款1,500萬贊助該計畫的研究，而美鐵的方案與7號地鐵的延伸計畫已經在資金的取得上形成競爭關係<ref>{{Cite news   | last = Higgss   | first = Larry   | title = Tunnelvision Gateway project, No. 7 train extension latest to vie for trans-Hudson blessing   | newspaper = Asbury Park Press   | date = 2011-12-04   | url = http://www.app.com/article/20111204/NJOPINION06/312040019/Gateway-project-No-7-line-extension-latest-vie-trans-Hudson-blessing?odyssey=nav%7Chead   | accessdate = 2011-12-05   | quote =    }}</ref>。

有鑑於預算方面的考量，大都會運輸署主席{{Link-en|喬·洛塔|Joe Lhota}}在2012年4月指出，無法確定地鐵7號線的過河工程是否能在短期內展開，並建議說美鐵的關口計畫是一個更容易達成的過河交通紓緩之道<ref>{{Cite news   | last = Haughney   | first = Christine   | title = MTA Chief rules out subway line to New Jersey   | newspaper = The New York Times   | date = 2012-04-03   | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/04/nyregion/transit-agency-chief-rules-out-new-york-new-jersey-subway.html?_r=1&scp=1&sq=7%20subway%20extension&st=cse   | accessdate = 2012-04-04   | quote =    }}</ref>。不過市府在2013年4月時委託製作的一分可行性研究書又重燃了該條地鐵延線的希望，彭博當時表示「7號地鐵的錫考克斯延伸線是一項大有可為的潛力方案...值得審慎考慮」<ref>[http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2013/04/plan_to_extend_no_7_city_subwa.html Plan to extend No. 7 subway from NYC to New Jersey could be back on track], Mike Frassinelli, The Star-Ledger, April 10, 2013</ref><ref name="nycedc 2">{{cite report   | author= Parsons Brinkerhoff   | title = No 7 Secaucus Extension Feasibility Analysis Final Report | publisher = NYCEDC   | date = April 2013   | url = http://www.nycedc.com/sites/default/files/filemanager/Resources/Studies/No_7_Secaucus_Extension_Final_Report_April_2013.pdf   | format = PDF   | accessdate = 2013-04-10 | page = III–X }}</ref>。

在2013年11月的一篇《[[紐約每日新聞|紐約每日新聞]]》觀點文章中，紐約不動產委員會會長和愛迪遜資產公司（{{lang|en|Edison Properties}}）主席呼籲將地鐵7號線的錫考克斯延伸段設計成與「關口計畫」的美鐵隧道共用<ref>{{cite news   | last = Gottesman   | first = Jerry   | last2 = Spinola   | first2 = Steven   | title = Let’s extend the 7 train to Secaucus After the far West Side, the next stop on the 7 should be across the river   | newspaper = Daily News   | date = 2013-11-04   | url = http://www.nydailynews.com/opinion/extend-7-train-secaucus-article-1.1504464   | accessdate = 2013-11-04   | quote = }}</ref>。同個月內，[[紐澤西州眾議院|紐澤西州眾議院]]過了一份168號決議案<ref>{{cite web   | title = AN ASSEMBLY RESOLUTION supporting the extension of the New York City IRT Flushing Line into the State of New Jersey.   | work = ASSEMBLY RESOLUTION No. 168 STATE OF NEW JERSEY 215th LEGISLATURE   | publisher = New Jersey Legislature   | date =2013-05-13| url = http://www.njleg.state.nj.us/2012/Bills/AR/168_I1.PDF   | format = PDF   | accessdate = 2013-11-26}}</ref>，支持紐約地鐵將7號線擴建到霍博肯和錫考克斯<ref>{{cite web   | last = Brenzel   | first = Kathryn   | title = Committee green lights expansion of NYC subway to Hoboken   | publisher = NJ.com   | date = 2013-11-26   | url = http://www.nj.com/hudson/index.ssf/2013/11/no_7_expansion.html#incart_river_default   | accessdate = 2013-11-26}}</ref>。
